{"tid":917704,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"點解冇人吹奏科幻劇Electric Dreams？","createTime":"2018-11-26T15:21:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T17:09:09.000Z","uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"177fcddf2613a3a842146f4151cbdff90b9f23e4","tid":917704,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T15:21:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/tabs.web.media/c/d/cd24/cd24-square-orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com%2Ftabs.web.media%2Fc%2Fd%2Fcd24%2Fcd24-square-orig.jpg&h=cb600a2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nElectric Dreams是一部英國科幻電視故事選系列劇，改編自菲利普&middot;狄克的作品。本劇於2017年9月17日在英國第四台上首播。本劇由十個基於菲利普&middot;狄克作品的獨立集數所組成。在美國，於亞馬遜影片上播放。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RtX_LVwEJhA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRtX_LVwEJhA&d=YooclASlctg8qEWrcGLfs10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=bfabcfb8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RtX_LVwEJhA</a><br />\n類似黑鏡既單元科幻劇，演員陣容電腦特技都唔算差，劇情上部分集數比得上黑鏡頭兩季，點解人氣同黑鏡差咁遠？"},{"pid":"795429fe2999d2d086c09aeba183ef31f008d408","tid":917704,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T15:24:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1e8d223052214272f21e04bf21125d7cc111f61","tid":917704,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"795429fe2999d2d086c09aeba183ef31f008d408","tid":917704,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T15:24:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T17:09:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}